{"messageId":"019d0fcad8cb755a9bd2383356143998","rawEvent":{"message_id":"019d0fcad8cb755a9bd2383356143998","conversation_id":"019d0f9fae89779db6ed36ac06200ef9","content":"

这个错误 `invalid character 'E' looking for beginning of object key string` 说明 JSON 反序列化时遇到了不带引号的键名（如 `EventV2Base` 而非 `"EventV2Base"`）。这意味着飞书 SDK 返回的数据实际上不是标准 JSON 格式，而是 Go 结构体的直接打印输出。

让我先看一下当前的代码，了解你是如何反序列化的。"},"timestamp":1774086451,"type":"TEXT_MESSAGE_CONTENT"}

{"messageId":"019d0fcad8cb755a9bd2383356143998","rawEvent":{"message_id":"019d0fcad8cb755a9bd2383356143998","conversation_id":"019d0f9fae89779db6ed36ac06200ef9","content":"找到问题了！在 [channel.go](/Users/weiketang/GolandProjects/self-agent/channel/channel.go) 第 89 行：

```go
if err := json.Unmarshal([]byte(larkcore.Prettify(event)), &eventData); err != nil {
```

**问题根因**：`larkcore.Prettify(event)` 输出的不是标准 JSON，而是 Go 结构体的美化打印格式（类似 `fmt.Sprintf("%+v", ...)`）。它的键名没有双引号包裹，所以 `json.Unmarshal` 遇到 `E`（`EventV2Base` 的首字母）时报错 `invalid character 'E' looking for beginning of object key string`。

**解决方案**：不要用 `larkcore.Prettify()`，而是直接从 `event` 对象的字段中提取数据。飞书 SDK 的 `*larkim.P2MessageReceiveV1` 本身就是一个 Go 结构体，可以直接读取字段。"},"timestamp":1774086458,"type":"TEXT_MESSAGE_CONTENT"}

{"rawEvent":{"message_id":"019d0fcad8cb755a9bd2383356143998","conversation_id":"019d0f9fae89779db6ed36ac06200ef9","tool_call_id":"tooluse_Xz9z95tWlT1Jbu5VQFDD6B","document":{"file_path":"/Users/weiketang/GolandProjects/self-agent/channel/channel.go","sub_content":"channel.go","sub_content_event":"open_editor","sub_content_event_value":"/Users/weiketang/GolandProjects/self-agent/channel/channel.go","sub_content_tip":"/Users/weiketang/GolandProjects/self-agent/channel/channel.go","old_string":"		OnP2MessageReceiveV1(func(ctx context.Context, event *larkim.P2MessageReceiveV1) error {
